Subject: [PATCH v12 11/17] media: uapi: Add V4L2_CID_STATELESS_HEVC_ENTRY_POINT_OFFSETS control
Date:   Fri,  8 Jul 2022 14:05:48 +0200
Message-Id: <20220708120554.495495-12-benjamin.gaignard@collabora.com>
